{"tid":1006914,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 咸錫轉會中超","createTime":"2019-02-03T11:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T18:37:58.000Z","uid":209051,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"fd24d04bfe3dcc6de383b7f452df408b88cc2676","tid":1006914,"uid":209051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"歐洲各大聯賽嘅冬季轉會市場已經完結，不過中超轉會窗仍然未閂，意大利周日(3號)更爆出驚人消息，拿玻里中場主力咸錫正同中超球會斟介，而且非常接近成事，據報呢位斯洛伐克球星將會同大連一方簽約3年，年薪高達900萬歐元。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拿玻里周日主場3比0贏森多利亞後，教練安察洛堤證實咸錫可能就快離隊：「轉會談判衣家正進行當中，咸錫喺拿玻里創造歷史，球會對佢非常尊重，如果佢想尋求新發展，我哋會盡量幫佢達成。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現年31歲嘅咸錫2007年加盟拿玻里，依家係球會史上入波最多(121球)同上陣最多(519場)球員，超越拿玻里名宿馬納當拿，絕對係拿玻里嘅傳奇。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曼聯幾年前都想收購咸錫，但未能成事，估唔到反而畀中超球會得手。內地媒體報道，大連一方向咸錫開出3年合約，原本拿玻里希望收到2,500萬歐元至3,000萬歐元轉會費，不過經多輪談判之後，最終只係<span style=\"color: red;\">1,500萬歐元</span>就成交。&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20190203/mobile/bkn-20190203120915800-0203_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20190203%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190203120915800-0203_00882_001.html&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7mHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=7432c4e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20190203/mobile/bkn-20190203120915800-0203_00882_001.html</a><br />\n正值當打之年仲要賣咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以佢實力同咁嘅價錢肯定仲有好多歐洲大球會要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed201064f486627ceec0e17cb7cd6b923cb71b4f","tid":1006914,"uid":26862,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:05:51.000Z","msg":"回哂塘啦"},{"pid":"be7e5f4ee28833ec09afd5b984181950756af80f","tid":1006914,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:06:54.000Z","msg":"咸錫朋友隊"},{"pid":"35f75b7fd6267b3868df89701db7bb879c855c58","tid":1006914,"uid":10014,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:08:33.000Z","msg":"拿破里黃金中場<br />\n<br />\n艾倫 佐真奴 咸錫"},{"pid":"ff9ad1aa82cfa82f8027279dc3f51c25e29cd81f","tid":1006914,"uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:09:44.000Z","msg":"當年死唔肯轉會"},{"pid":"bebd4c545a43fb64f3edb760b453fc82626c7f17","tid":1006914,"uid":125530,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:10:17.000Z","msg":"條友都幾慘，國家隊又廢，踢意甲就成世俾祖記食住"},{"pid":"d97c8cb6daac019a55534f286d0a2ab2281fe29c","tid":1006914,"uid":185092,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:13:43.000Z","msg":"好鍾意佢髮型"},{"pid":"94ce754c50894991ae0239d539dce349c7ab285b","tid":1006914,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:15:32.000Z","msg":"沙狗唔買埋佢？"},{"pid":"f95f71cf2d10290ff20947d831d2bb27b1f182a0","tid":1006914,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:16:04.000Z","msg":"當年巴黎想買埋佢，買極都買唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7395e6dd549099bc33a2641a96411060f027a48","tid":1006914,"uid":34772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:17:15.000Z","msg":"又話佢唔走係因為有黑手黨唔比佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d172402b41824051b3a00bf7cc7dd326ec63f111","tid":1006914,"uid":132262,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:18:54.000Z","msg":"樓主，31歲當打之年？"},{"pid":"2da478a43d43bb12ffa08068be28cbe5f0b27750","tid":1006914,"uid":5649,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"b7395e6dd549099bc33a2641a96411060f027a48","tid":1006914,"uid":34772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:17:15.000Z","msg":"又話佢唔走係因為有黑手黨唔比佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:20:05.000Z","msg":"全球最大黑幫屌打黑撚黨"},{